OL,5, The #2 cap on bus fares has been       
OL,6, extended for three months following    
OL,7, warnings that hundreds of services     
OL,8, could be cut if it ended.              
OL,10,FThe cap applies to more than 130 bus   
OL,11,Foperators outside London.              
OL,13,FIt had been due to expire on 31 March, 
OL,14,Fbut has been extended until the end of 
OL,15,FJune.                                  
OL,17,FBus operators have been struggling to  
OL,18,Fmaintain service levels in the face of 
OL,19,Frising costs and passenger numbers not 
OL,20,Frecovering to pre-pandemic levels.     
